    <PrimAttribute name="sourceDirectory" id="81906148-e96f-481a-b8fd-41133f22ace5">
        <type name="String"/>
        <access>readonly</access>
        <text>
IMPORTANT 
- for outging messages this is the local directory where
the outging message is copied from.  Note that this is ignored
for CAMS processing as it takes the file from whereever CAMS has 
put it (refer to Terminal Config).

- for incoming messages (which are not handled yet) this 
would be the directory on the FTP server that the message is
copied from.</text>
    </PrimAttribute>
